     Perl-Critic(2) tool.

   - *note sh-shellcheck: 129. checks Shell scripts with the awesome
     Shellcheck(3) tool, which finds all sorts of idiomatic and
     semantics mistakes in shell scripts of various shell languages,
     and will greatly improve your shell scripting.

D users can now tell *note d-dmd: b8. about include directories with the
new option *note flycheck-dmd-include-path: b9.  Likewise, Rust users
can use *note flycheck-rust-library-path: 11b. now.

